OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStudents to pay off loans  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finto their 60s, plans say  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Students who start university next year
OL,6, could be paying off their loans for 40 
OL,7, years after graduating, under new      
OL,8, government plans for England.          
OL,10,FUnder the current system, loans are    
OL,11,Fwritten off after 30 years.            
OL,13,FThe government says extending the      
OL,14,Frepayment period, as part of a student 
OL,15,Ffinance shake-up, will reduce the bill 
OL,16,Ffor taxpayers.                         
OL,18,FBut Labour says it will "hit those on  
OL,19,Flow incomes hardest", with             
OL,20,Flower-earning graduates affected more. 
